cdata.name: MMNXT
cdata.desc:
MMNXT is a NXT asset that paid dividends to holders and works as an automated trading fund for NXT asset exchange. MMNXT has recently merged with EIX and formed the NEXT asset. Even though MMNXT does not pay dividends and is no longer swappable for NEXT, it can be freely traded in the regular exchange markets.

Asset ID: 979292558519844732
